---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Creative Compass — River Roots Studio" description="A way of listening to your gut feeling — that intuition beyond your brain's accounting. Discover the Creative Compass at River Roots Studio.">
  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="relative bg-moss/10 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-moss mb-3 leading-tight">
        The Creative Compass
      </h1>
      <p class="font-heading text-xl sm:text-2xl text-terracotta italic">
        A way of listening to your gut feeling — that intuition beyond your brain&rsquo;s accounting.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OPENING QUOTE -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <blockquote>
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-4 text-terracotta/40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M4.583 17.321C3.553 16.227 3 15 3 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179zm10 0C13.553 16.227 13 15 13 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179z" />
        </svg>
        <p class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-brown italic leading-relaxed mb-3">
          Art is not a thing, it&rsquo;s a way.
        </p>
        <footer class="text-brown/60">
          <cite class="not-italic text-sm">&mdash; Elbert Hubbard</cite>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEXTANT IMAGE + BODY CONTENT -->
  <section class="pb-10 sm:pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
        <img
          src="/images/workshop-sextant.png"
          alt="A hand-drawn sextant — finding your bearings through creative exploration"
          class="max-w-xs w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-brown/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          A Creative Compass is like taking &ldquo;A Map with No Names&rdquo; and giving it longitude
          and latitude. It&rsquo;s for those longing for wonder and aching for enriched lives — a way
          of orienting yourself toward what matters most, even when the path isn&rsquo;t yet clear.
        </p>
        <p>
          River Roots workshops weave together Expressive Arts, Spiritual Direction, and Ritual.
          Through natural elements — poetry, music, collage, writing, and tactile making — we move
          through three phases together: <strong class="text-moss font-semibold">ROOT. FLOW. BECOME.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ROOT. FLOW. BECOME. -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-12 bg-moss/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
        <img
          src="/images/root-flow-become.png"
          alt="Root, Flow, Become — the three phases of a River Roots workshop journey"
          class="max-w-[280px] w-full h-auto"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-brown/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-moss font-semibold">ROOT:</strong> We settle into the body and the
          present moment, releasing the noise of the everyday.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-moss font-semibold">FLOW:</strong> We let the materials lead, following
          intuition rather than intention.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-moss font-semibold">BECOME:</strong> We witness what has emerged and
          carry it forward into daily life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING BLESSING -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-12 bg-moss/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="font-heading text-xl sm:text-2xl text-brown italic leading-relaxed mb-8">
        I send you a wish, a prayer, and a blessing that will inspire you to take many expeditions
        into unknown paths — and be surprised by magic.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/workshops"
        class="inline-block bg-terracotta hover:bg-terracotta-dark text-cream px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-medium text-lg transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-terracotta focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-cream"
      >
        Experience it yourself &rarr; See Workshops
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
